es.ed0.tinyjson.parser

Class JSONUrlReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • es.ed0.tinyjson.parser.JSONUrlReader

  • public class JSONUrlReader
extends java.lang.Object
    Class for reading and parsing json objects and arrays from a URL resource.
    Request headers or extra parameters may be included using addRequestHeader(String, String) and addParameter(String, String) respectively
